{"tid":1661392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司法機構將罕有地安排兩名法官共審理政府引用《緊急法》","createTime":"2019-10-18T05:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T07:17:21.000Z","uid":151924,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"44338b3c68852be8d48d7a69e16cbb5bf4890cd2","tid":1661392,"uid":151924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T05:20:15.000Z","msg":"24 名民主派立法會議員及社民連梁國雄早前分別入禀高等法院申請司法覆核，挑戰政府引用《緊急法》訂立《禁蒙面法》, 兩案將於本月 31 日合併審理。《南華早報》及評論人 David Webb 昨日（17日）均引述消息指，司法機構將罕有地安排兩名法官共同審理此案，除審理臨時禁制令時的法官林雲浩外，法官周家明亦會加入審理阿案件 ...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8-%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%93%E7%AB%8B%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E7%BD%95%E6%9C%89%E9%81%A3%E5%85%A9%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E5%AF%A9%E7%90%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25BD%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2581%25A3%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E7%2590%2586%2F&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=928da77a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25BD%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2581%25A3%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E7%2590%2586%2F&h=b196e59c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8-%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%93%E7%AB